{"tid":2362103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係旺角弼街stm group見工？係咪有伏","createTime":"2021-01-11T08:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T09:12:45.000Z","uid":128752,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4b0b7471524503a4f9a8789505f7479fa4d5b5","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"上到去見到勁多人目測30人左右<br />\n有d係一group人傾野咁<br />\n有d係一對一傾<br />\n唔係正常office係一排排長枱<br />\n門口附近有6張枱一對一interview<br />\n除左我都有4-5個都in緊<br />\n個經理會係張白紙介紹係做咩marketing工作<br />\n話咩有前線亦有back office<br />\n但係聽完都係唔知做乜9<br />\n得左會有個一星期無paid既training <br />\n想問係咪呃人傳銷9?<br />\n<br />\n最奇怪係黨鐵站等會帶埋你上去<br />\n走又會帶你行番大街到做乜9"},{"pid":"1344af2bcf06e943ef8201c7c99c2e4a4fa9230d","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5491452643fca342aff310baf184697cd6b707","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d3c44a11490d1fcfeaa2ac96ccd278b2ab88f6f","tid":2362103,"uid":75311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"有陣傳銷味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268d99cd9e3537c951a178baceea3b2f0a327fe3","tid":2362103,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"傳銷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9795bc185c4e7b2b8e50e46072807839cb96b25e","tid":2362103,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"100%傳銷"},{"pid":"a7b9e70e942b415268c44c44d3c16d0e8350cf50","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d3c44a11490d1fcfeaa2ac96ccd278b2ab88f6f","tid":2362103,"uid":75311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"有陣傳銷味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"諗住走個陣可以同隔離其他見工討論下<br />\n點知條友話帶埋你落去驚我唔識路"},{"pid":"31ff1be750682307fc42a182080dd4187aef5b95","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"推比多d人知"},{"pid":"ec5471b921f5f17128482b01f6dfa050a87d300b","tid":2362103,"uid":374602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"816fb45dc73b1fcf87d3bd03be0246dbb0e1a635","tid":2362103,"uid":242736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"如果早少少見到你個post我就唔洗on99聽條友講九個字廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8daf9b274975ae3d04bcbc9e496129836373ce","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"816fb45dc73b1fcf87d3bd03be0246dbb0e1a635","tid":2362103,"uid":242736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"如果早少少見到你個post我就唔洗on99聽條友講九個字廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"推俾人知，其實個過程已經係有問題，公司都俾唔到人仲要帶上去"},{"pid":"15e092b00725255f6db8f76a98d359b9efbdc6b7","tid":2362103,"uid":242736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7583d67d18af4e33592a8dc820a399e3bcf8116f","tid":2362103,"uid":325115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"啱啱我收到電費叫我去in 都唔知咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇多啲資料 interview究竟會問啲咩"},{"pid":"acd3e5561ab4994a69316094bf43d7177a525087","tid":2362103,"uid":242736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7583d67d18af4e33592a8dc820a399e3bcf8116f","tid":2362103,"uid":325115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"re