img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁奇怪 唔該哂你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8716fa5ac55436dbe07eae8d80adb029f61e451f","tid":2362103,"uid":325115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d42f034bae0d05d99f08bd829112cf09dfbc7a","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7583d67d18af4e33592a8dc820a399e3bcf8116f","tid":2362103,"uid":325115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"啱啱我收到電費叫我去in 都唔知咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇多啲資料 interview究竟會問啲咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:12:29.000Z","msg":"唔使去，慳返時間仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T15:06:59.000Z","msg":"好 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個HR啱啱突登wts問我係咪聽日interview<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係唔去了"},{"pid":"e761b5ae5daace48bfee16363f94aec3827e29c4","tid":2362103,"uid":390000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"我有個frd上晒啲training，但係佢講返俾我知嘅時候我就覺得間野好伏，但係我唔識點同佢解釋有咩問題，因為佢依家的確係冇叫佢俾錢買任何product ，但係我覺得佢好明顯係傳銷，仲話自己唔係傳銷係直銷🙄🙄<br />\n<br />\n有冇ching可以幫手解釋一下🙏🙏🙏<br />\n等我可以話返俾我朋友知"},{"pid":"777ac8c96aba5190895e6653622957aafa78b46b","tid":2362103,"uid":390000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef8daf9b274975ae3d04bcbc9e496129836373ce","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"816fb45dc73b1fcf87d3bd03be0246dbb0e1a635","tid":2362103,"uid":242736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"如果早少少見到你個post我就唔洗on99聽條友講九個字廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"推俾人知，其實個過程已經係有問題，公司都俾唔到人仲要帶上去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"想問一下佢係點呃人？"},{"pid":"6f40964151a9c4130ae4f4b3dbf7cffc8acd889a","tid":2362103,"uid":200227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"On9 傳銷 哂時間"},{"pid":"b577c3a52b53cb95993e86ce4383bdea7d83c2d1","tid":2362103,"uid":200227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb0ce0ac22655481926bf7163e59a33709b9bf7f","tid":2362103,"uid":242736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"777ac8c96aba5190895e6653622957aafa78b46b","tid":2362103,"uid":390000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef8daf9b274975ae3d04bcbc9e496129836373ce","tid":2362103,"uid":128752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"816fb45dc73b1fcf87d3bd03be0246dbb0e1a635","tid":2362103,"uid":242736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"如果早少少見到你個post我就唔洗on99聽條友講九個字廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"推俾人知，其實個過程已經係有問題，公司都俾唔到人仲要帶上去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"想問一下佢係點呃人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"佢係打嚟話你問你有冇興趣見工 然後會有條友扮熟同你傾下計咁 之後就約你in interview過程就講左啦 但睇佢所謂office都似係傳銷狗公司嚟 得幾張長枱同你講話係interview day先係咁 再落去我都唔知了 我一in完就即係收佢皮"},{"pid":"5a460c4fb79aa8ba3317be5c5f56c6136f218d6c","tid":2362103,"uid":200227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"其實呃人都賺幾多錢"},{"pid":"0356c2c68a33542ac2c1fcdef8393e5264c6c174","tid":2362103,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"以下呢間？<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span class=\"green\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=81c98e16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=72cb4895\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=7b9984ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXuxBB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXuxBB7.png&h=dffa07b7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}